snippet.title: Parking Garage Rally Circuit Release Date Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Parking Garage Rally Circuit is my arcade precision driving game about rally racing in parking garages across the USA, presented like a Sega Saturn game from ~1998.

Releasing on September 20, 2024 on Steam for Windows and Linux / Steam Deck!

Featuring an all-original soundtrack by The Holophonics, including the song "Another Level" used in this trailer.

Wishlist on Steam today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2737300/Parking_Garage_Rally_Circuit/

#indiegame #retrogaming #rally #segasaturn
